list.name: Default
list.comment: Fixed a bug in the helper is_user_owns_resource() function where resource object retrieved for the given resource_id can be null. The code now checks if the retrieved resource object is null or not before using accessing any properties of this object.

task.summary: Fix to the problem of sending a bigger ueb model package to the app server.
Fix to the problem of apache server going down due to sqlalchemy session pool limit problem as a result of running background scheduled tasks.
Updated to allow user to select files as input for various variables/parameters of UEB when configuring the model to create a model package.

Fixed the bug for listing files in ueb package builder and ueb run where files not owned by the user also used to get listed. Also new job status types returned from the app server were accounted for. The problem of App scheduler running at random interval was fixed.

New helper method for getting a list of datasets (with resources) for a given dataset type. Shape files are now loaded for selection in UEB package build configuration based on dataset 'type' = 'geographic-feature-set' and resource file format = 'zip'.
Added the extension pycharm iml fil2
Package builder now saves the package build request as dataset type 'model-configuration' and saves the model package zip file as 'model-package.

Fixed a bug in the helper is_user_owns_resource() function where resource object retrieved for the given resource_id can be null. The code now checks if the retrieved resource object is null or not before using accessing any properties of this object.
